block content
	.container-sm: .pv-2
		h1!=errorTitle || 'PAGE NOT FOUND'
		if 'object' == typeof errorMsg
			div(style='margin: 30px 0;').debug!= htmlStringify(errorMsg)
		else
			p.lead!= utils.textToHTML(errorMsg) || 'Whoops, that page is missing!'

If you clicked a link that led you to this page, please let us know so we can fix our mistake as soon as possible.'
